title: Byron Froese scores shootout winner to lead Marlies past Moose 3-2 (NHL - National Hockey ...
text: ( Source : NHL - National Hockey League ) TORONTO - Byron Froese scored the only goal of the shootout and added another in regulation as the Toronto Marlies edged the Manitoba Moose 3-2 on Saturday afternoon in American Hockey League action.
